^\[main\.p5w\] main\.x == 0 \[=2\]: PROVED$
^\[main\.p4s\] strong\(main\.x == 0 \[->2\]\): PROVED$
^\[main\.p5s\] strong\(main\.x == 0 \[=2\]\): PROVED$
